{"tid":2185712,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"꧁突發꧂Dragon's Dogma龍族教義動畫化，9月17日Netflix全球同步推出","createTime":"2020-09-02T12:29:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T13:52:21.000Z","uid":38539,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a27f93511189e86f173de22641af346bab5dfcc","tid":2185712,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efq8ggI3xdg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Defq8ggI3xdg&d=5n7Vw74FaX2H6oE8X5RxXC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=045d70e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=efq8ggI3xdg</a><br />\n係今年STEAM 夏日減價買咗隻GAME玩完依家就就出動畫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Dragon's Dogma 龍族教義》為日本 Capcom（卡普空）自 2012 年起陸續推出，由《惡魔獵人》開發者「小林裕幸」與「伊津野英昭」分別擔任製作人與遊戲總監，以劍與魔法為主題，系列累計出貨超過 470 萬套以上的高幻想風第三人稱視點動作 RPG 系列。<br />\n敵龍壓倒性的強大而失敗，心臟更被龍爪所取出奪走。原本應該死亡的主角，卻因為成為被龍所選中的「覺者」而再度甦醒，並為了奪回自己的心臟而展開旅程&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n而在這次由 Netflix 於之前 2019 年 3 月就公開，日本 Sublimation 負責製作的動畫版部分，將從主角「Ethan」為守護家人對抗來襲的龍，卻反而被龍奪去心臟，並以「覺者」之姿再度甦醒。為了奪回心臟，他將與名為「Hannah」的金髮女性「隨從」（Pawn）一起踏上旅程，對抗代表七大罪的怪物，隨著主角每打倒一頭怪物，自己的人性亦會隨之逐漸消逝&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"cd22c976214e475bba70944c042792b85d8af823","tid":2185712,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:29:47.000Z","msg":"以為隻online game 翻生"},{"pid":"30526964f0c9bf5ba56b7586fea0e109f63290be","tid":2185712,"uid":200230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"個符號你點打的"},{"pid":"a692ef5a98c17fddebf23ddb61ee9a007d51a075","tid":2185712,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30526964f0c9bf5ba56b7586fea0e109f63290be","tid":2185712,"uid":200230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:29:57.000Z","msg":"個符號你點打的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-02T12:31:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unicodes.smpc.io/\" data-sr-url=\"h